d55f7be5a4dd2090098ebe59c5d25452e7e972f","tid":457182,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日好多都食品飲品都有事<br />\n但人地肯改</blockquote><br />\n雪印都衰過幾單<br />\n<br />\n就算有呢啲新聞 包括神戶鋼鐵嗰啲嘢<br />\n我都信日本製造多過支那製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5620629080ae78ce3b71e862107c42cac1eed8","tid":457182,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dfeda59f8e1c96aaaf5152d471ddb055d6b1caa","tid":457182,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日好多都食品飲品都有事<br />\n但人地肯改</blockquote><br />\n雪印都衰過幾單<br />\n<br />\n就算有呢啲新聞 包括神戶鋼鐵嗰啲嘢<br />\n我都信日本製造多過支那製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係崇日但日本仔起碼肯道歉先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗侵華<br />\n呢樣真係扣哂分 班右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62538df3853cba7e447f4fdc4674f6984f56e735","tid":457182,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:15:09.000Z","msg":"崇日撚正辣撒"},{"pid":"b4d472dd849ac8812ee55107e3216a8abfdd7fd3","tid":457182,"uid":69614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:34:25.000Z","msg":"如果淨係得一個證實有問題既明星杯麵<br />\n同一個康師x 杯麵<br />\n而我又好肚餓<br />\n我都係會食明星杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821f54389514bf5fea280e6af3862dca950e23de","tid":457182,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"日本是神聖的<br />\n樓豬轉貼假新聞可恥"},{"pid":"5b9a0c44ec9220b3f2008fc07b33a